data.description: An assumable VA mortgage is now available at an interest rate of 2.75%!  This opportunity is specific to VA loans, enabling eligible veterans to take over the mortgage with the same interest rate, repayment period, and monthly payment as the current owner.   Loan application and approval still apply.  Welcome to this beautiful two-story home located in the heart of Niceville!   Built in 2013, this traditional-style home is nestled on a picturesque corner lot with stone accents and pretty curb appeal.  The main floor features an open living, kitchen, and dining area creating an ideal space for family gatherings or entertaining friends.  You will also find lovely built-in bookshelves in the living area adding character and functionality. On the second floor you will find the large master suite providing enough space for a sitting area, master bath with garden tub, and a large walk-in closet.  In addition, the second floor offers flexible open space that can be used as an office, playroom, or workout room, providing versatility to suit your lifestyle.  This home is also equipped with a tankless water heater, an energy-efficient upgrade providing unlimited hot water on demand and reduced energy costs.  Step outside to a private, fenced-in backyard with mature trees and a patio area where you can enjoy outdoor activities and relax.  This home is not part of a homeowner association community, and there are no homeowner association dues, offering you the freedom to enjoy your property without additional financial obligations.  This home has been impeccably cared for and is in pristine condition, ensuring a move-in ready experience for its new owners.  Attention, investors! This property is a prime candidate for long-term rentals, thanks to its close proximity to military bases. A comprehensive rental report can be obtained upon request.  The popular town of Niceville offers easy access to military bases, local schools, shopping, dining, and recreational opportunities. The area is known for its friendly atmosphere and welcoming community.  Don't miss this incredible opportunity to make this beautiful two-story house your forever home.
